"    Mesorectum - Male pelvis lateral view",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 453px; height: 558px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    This figure depicts the lateral view of the male pelvis,&nbsp;illustrating the relationship of the mesorectum to the posterior rectum and presacral space. The mesorectum is&nbsp; not a true mesentery, but rather is perirectal areolar tissue that is thicker posteriorly and contains terminal branches of the inferior mesenteric artery.",
