"    Alcoholic steatohepatitis (lower power, Masson trichrome)",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 432px; height: 252px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    In addition to fat-filled hepatocytes, there are swollen necrotic hepatocytes and early scarring and inflammation.",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
"    </div>",
"    <div class=\"reference\">",
"     Courtesy of Marshall M. Kaplan, MD.",
"    </div>",
"   </div>",
"  </div>",
" </div>",
